# My-portfolio-
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Shubham Mishra | Portfolio</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#0f172a;
    color:white;
}

header{
    text-align:center;
    padding:50px 20px;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2563eb,#06b6d4);
}

.profile{
    width:180px;
    height:180px;
    border-radius:50%;
    border:5px solid white;
    object-fit:cover;
}

h1{
    margin-top:15px;
    font-size:3rem;
}

.tagline{
    font-size:1.2rem;
    margin-top:10px;
}

nav{
    background:#111827;
    text-align:center;
    padding:15px;
}

nav a{
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    margin:15px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

section{
    max-width:1000px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:40px 20px;
}

.card{
    background:#1e293b;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:15px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.skills{
    display:flex;
    flex-wrap:wrap;
    gap:10px;
}

.skill{
    background:#2563eb;
    padding:10px 15px;
    border-radius:20px;
}

footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:20px;
    background:#111827;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <img src="myphoto.jpg" class="profile" alt="My Photo">
    <h1>Shubham Mishra</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Class 8 Student | Science Lover | Future Programmer</p>
</header>

<nav>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
    <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
    <a href="#achievements">Achievements</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section id="about">
    <div class="card">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
            Hello! I am Shubham Mishra, a Class 8 student.
            I enjoy Science, Mathematics, Geography and Computer Programming.
            I love creating projects and learning new technologies.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="skills">
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <div class="skills">
            <div class="skill">HTML</div>
            <div class="skill">Python</div>
            <div class="skill">Science Projects</div>
            <div class="skill">Mathematics</div>
            <div class="skill">Public Speaking</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="projects">
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Chandrayaan-3 Science Exhibition Project</li>
            <li>Simple Electric Circuit Model</li>
            <li>Geography Scrapbook Project</li>
            <li>Python Programming Practice</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="achievements">
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Achievements</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Participated in School Science Exhibition</li>
            <li>Completed Multiple School Projects</li>
            <li>Learning Web Development</li>
            <li>Developing Python Programming Skills</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Name: Shubham Mishra</p>
        <p>School: Pride International School, Narkatiaganj</p>
        <p>Class: 8</p>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Shubham Mishra Portfolio</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
